## ðŸ” What is a Prompt Engineer?

A Prompt Engineer is a professional who specializes in designing, testing, and refining inputs (prompts) given to AI systems like ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, etc. Think of prompts as the "Standard Operating Procedures (SOPs)" of the AI world â€” they determine how accurately, efficiently, and responsibly the AI will behave.

They arenâ€™t just writing instructions â€” theyâ€™re designing thought processes for machines.

